(39926, 120253, 0, 1, 'Whispering', 'A song for a cat and a laid-back afternoon.', '2011-10-18 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 7, 'I am only sleeping, I''m not waiting for you to come.\r\nDrifting, floating in the space. Watch the people run, below my eyes.\r\n\r\nI let the time flow like a river, I let the times go by.\r\nAnd you know that all I need is a place to hide.\r\n\r\nAlone, but not lonely, got no place to go, I''ve got no soul.\r\nYou said everyone needs someone just being out there.\r\n\r\nYou wanna be my my friend, and you told me you''ve got something want to share.\r\nAnd you mean I am the one, but I''m not there.\r\nYou''re hanging around me but won''t you please, just leave me alone.\r\nNo love no glory, and nothing will be told.\r\n\r\nCan''t you see? Just leave me alone, I''ll be alright.\r\n\r\nIf you hang around, you''re wasting your time.', '', 321, '', 'Hence & Comma', 'Hence & Comma', 'Hence & Comma', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2011-10-18 17:48:29', '2015-03-12 13:48:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
